'''''August Underground's Mordum''''' is an [[indie|independent]] film which teaches the value of [[Incest|family togetherness]].

The single most [[AWESOME|sickening, disgusting, and gruesome]] piece of shit EVAR. August Underground's ''Mordum'' has made it onto more "Ten Sickest Movies" lists than you can imagine, and for good reason. It is a faux [[snuff film]], shot entirely with a [[Cloverfield|camcorder]], with no discernible plot or direction; just plenty of raep, murder, vomit, and blood. Oh yeah, and corpses. Lots of those. And Extremely disappointing. 

